## L2 MockMvc

`standaloneSetup(controller)`，权限仍在 L1 测。Spacetime 统一 JUnit 5：`@ExtendWith(MockitoExtension)` + `@BeforeEach`。

```java
@Test
void route_正常() throws Exception {
    mockMvc.perform(post("/admin/xxx").header("X-Auth-Token", "test-token")
            .contentType(MediaType.APPLICATION_JSON).content("{}"))
        .andExpect(status().isOk()).andExpect(jsonPath("$.code").value(200));
}
@Test
void route_缺参() throws Exception {
    mockMvc.perform(post("/admin/xxx")).andExpect(status().isBadRequest());
}
@Test
void route_未登录() throws Exception {
    mockMvc.perform(get("/admin/xxx")).andExpect(status().isUnauthorized());
}
```

